quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  8,65,"Yewe Muhanuzi (Muhamadi)! Shishikariza abemeramana kwitabira urugamba. Muri mwe, nihabamo makumyabiri bihangana, bazatsinda magana abiri. Kandi nihabamo ijana, bazatsinda igihumbi muri ba bandi bahakanye, kubera ko ari abantu badasobanukiwe"
  8,66,"Ubu noneho Allah araborohereje, kandi azi ko mwifitemo intege nke. Bityo muri mwe nihabamo ijana bihangana, bazatsinda magana abiri. Kandi nihabamo igihumbi bazatsinda ibihumbi bibiri ku bushake bwa Allah. Rwose Allah ari kumwe n'abihangana"
  8,67,"Ntibikwiye ko umuhanuzi yagira imfungwa z’intambara, keretse amaze kwizera ko yatsinze urugamba. Murashaka indonke z’isi (muhabwa incungu kuri izo mfungwa zo ku rugamba rw’ i Bad’ri), kandi Allah ashaka (ko mubona ingororano) z’imperuka. Rwose, Allah ni Umunyacyubahiro bihebuje, Nyirubugenge buhambaye"
  8,68,"Iyo bitaza kuba itegeko rya Allah ryabanje (ribemerera iminyago no kugira imfungwa z’intambara), mwari kugerwaho n’ibihano bihambaye kubera ibyo mwakiriye (incungu)"
  8,69,"Ngaho nimurye mu minyago mwafashe, iziruwe kandi myiza. Munatinye Allah; mu by'ukuri, Allah ni Ubabarira ibyaha, Nyirimpuhwe"